{"tid":2098005,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警證供矛盾 監工拒捕罪脫","createTime":"2020-07-07T07:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T09:06:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e8586c39833feca1f04b0ee8831ab15ea9d4d98","tid":2098005,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:36:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/HSQQYOJG3P2GDPNEHBJWMVKRK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FHSQQYOJG3P2GDPNEHBJWMVKRK4%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivae24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=2c5b856f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FHSQQYOJG3P2GDPNEHBJWMVKRK4%2F&h=40179869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/HSQQYOJG3P2GDPNEHBJWMVKRK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警證供矛盾 監工拒捕罪脫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_r-amsa03iG9QBYY1_MLE7wV9To=/640x376/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7QAKXNTHNSVLDOEGPK55DNPWKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_r-amsa03iG9QBYY1_MLE7wV9To%3D%2F640x376%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7QAKXNTHNSVLDOEGPK55DNPWKE.jpg&h=b9bf97f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警長楊希勤<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】水務署監工被指<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n，裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n截停被告行為有多個版本<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：逼網絡商提供用戶身份<br />\n<br />\n25歲<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據警長楊希勤昨供稱，<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n軍裝警到場拘捕被告。<br />\n<br />\n惟楊在辯方盤問下就截停控制被告的行為說了多個版本。楊的書面證供指出示委任證後，被告想轉身離開，他才搭住被告膊頭阻他離開。楊庭上則稱「其實動作係同時間做」，並指不見被告有傷勢。<br />\n<br />\n到場增援的軍裝警員7234作供卻稱兩人均有傷勢，被告上衣被扯爛、右臂有六厘米擦損。而港鐵職員區嘉喬供稱中年男子捉住黑衣人前從沒表露身份、也沒展示過委任證，是雙方停止拉扯後才出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官林子勤昨裁定表證成立，聽取雙方陳詞後隨即裁決。林官指留意到警長的證供前後矛盾，書面供詞顯示被告轉身與他捉着被告有因果關係，明顯與接受控方主問時說法不符，追問下未能提出合理解釋，說法亦與港鐵職員證供有出入，認為控方案情中的關鍵情節帶有疑點，裁定被告脫罪。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC4232/19"},{"pid":"b470347a7f830af6cee1501b1f83a1db08740ce1","tid":2098005,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:38:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>近日新增大量本地確診</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家出街一定要戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n勤力洗手<br />\n<br />\n唔好去人多既地方</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">希望政府可以立即停課，收緊限聚令，停gym房，戲院，k房等</span></span>"},{"pid":"627cae41e488b38b81388c94c5878b9f30953fc7","tid":2098005,"uid":256019,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:40:34.000Z","msg":"個新聞標題用&quot;罪脫&quot;已經有問題，明明係罪名不成立，被講到明明有罪，但狡計逃脫咁款！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8834b9f3e010ee9afb6f00bad00f0b09e016035a","tid":2098005,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:06:30.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}